kathleen marie " kathy " garver ( born december 13 , 1945 ) is an american stage , film , television , and voice - over actress most remembered for having portrayed the teenage niece , catherine " cissy " davis , to series character uncle bill davis , played by brian keith , on the popular 1960s cbs sitcom , family affair .

